title: Come Join Our Friendly Discord!!

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body:
Hey Guys!
anyone who wants to find some team mates for competitive flex, or just to have some norms fun, Our discord server is the perfect place for it!
we have a friendly, welcoming server with over 30 active (league playing) members.. ranging from bronze to diamond
The server itself has a wide variety of plugins that make it more unique and interesting
trollers will be banned
cool peeps are welcome
https://discord.gg/ZAzkp8w
have fun ;)
